    <verse number="68" style="v" sid="EZR 2:68" />¶ And <char style="add">some</char> of the <char style="w" strong="H7218">chief</char> of the <char style="w" strong="H0001">fathers</char>, when they <char style="w" strong="H0935">came</char> to the <char style="w" strong="H1004">house</char> of the <char style="nd"><char style="w" strong="H3068">LORD</char></char> which <char style="add">is</char> at <char style="w" strong="H3389">Jerusalem</char>, offered <char style="w" strong="H5068">freely</char> for the <char style="w" strong="H1004">house</char> of <char style="w" strong="H0430">God</char> to set it <char style="w" strong="H5975">up</char> in his <char style="w" strong="H4349">place</char>: <verse eid="EZR 2:68" /><verse number="69" style="v" sid="EZR 2:69" />They <char style="w" strong="H5414">gave</char> after their <char style="w" strong="H3581">ability</char> unto the <char style="w" strong="H0214">treasure</char> of the <char style="w" strong="H4399">work</char> <char style="w" strong="H8337">threescore</char> and one <char style="w" strong="H0505">thousand</char> <char style="w" strong="H1871">drams</char> of <char style="w" strong="H2091">gold</char>, and <char style="w" strong="H2568">five</char> <char style="w" strong="H0505">thousand</char> <char style="w" strong="H4488">pound</char> of <char style="w" strong="H3701">silver</char>, and one <char style="w" strong="H3967">hundred</char> <char style="w" strong="H3548">priests’</char> <char style="w" strong="H3801">garments</char>. <verse eid="EZR 2:69" /><verse number="70" style="v" sid="EZR 2:70" />So the <char style="w" strong="H3548">priests</char>, and the <char style="w" strong="H3881">Levites</char>, and <char style="add">some</char> of the <char style="w" strong="H5971">people</char>, and the <char style="w" strong="H7891">singers</char>, and the <char style="w" strong="H7778">porters</char>, and the <char style="w" strong="H5411">Nethinims</char>, <char style="w" strong="H3427">dwelt</char> in their <char style="w" strong="H5892">cities</char>, and all <char style="w" strong="H3478">Israel</char> in their <char style="w" strong="H5892">cities</char>.<verse eid="EZR 2:70" /></para>
