char style="add">offered</char> the <char style="w" strong="H8548">continual</char> burnt <char style="w" strong="H5930">offering</char>, both of the new <char style="w" strong="H2320">moons</char>, and of all the set <char style="w" strong="H4150">feasts</char> of the <char style="nd"><char style="w" strong="H3068">LORD</char></char> that were <char style="w" strong="H6942">consecrated</char>, and of every one that willingly <char style="w" strong="H5068">offered</char> a freewill <char style="w" strong="H5071">offering</char> unto the <char style="nd"><char style="w" strong="H3068">LORD</char></char>. <verse eid="EZR 3:5" /><verse number="6" style="v" sid="EZR 3:6" />From the <char style="w" strong="H0259">first</char> <char style="w" strong="H3117">day</char> of the <char style="w" strong="H7637">seventh</char> <char style="w" strong="H2320">month</char> <char style="w" strong="H2490">began</char> they to <char style="w" strong="H5927">offer</char> burnt <char style="w" strong="H5930">offerings</char> unto the <char style="nd"><char style="w" strong="H3068">LORD</char></char>. But the <char style="w" strong="H3245">foundation</char> of the <char style="w" strong="H1964">temple</char> of the <char style="nd"><char style="w" strong="H3068">LORD</char></char> was not <char style="add">yet</char> <char style="w" strong="H3245">laid</char>.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">3.6 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">the foundation…: Heb. the temple of the </char><char style="nd" closed="false" /><char style="ft" closed="false">LORD</char><unmatched marker="+nd*" /> was not yet founded</note> <verse eid="EZR 3:6" /><verse number="7" style="v" sid="EZR 3:7" />They <char style="w" strong="H5414">gave</char> <char style="w" strong="H3701">money</char> also unto the <char style="w" strong="H2672">masons</char>, and to the <char style="w" strong="H2796">carpenters</char>; and <char style="w" strong="H3978">meat</char>, and <char style="w" strong="H49