  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="EZR 3:8" />¶ Now in the <char style="w" strong="H8145">second</char> <char style="w" strong="H8141">year</char> of their <char style="w" strong="H0935">coming</char> unto the <char style="w" strong="H1004">house</char> of <char style="w" strong="H0430">God</char> at <char style="w" strong="H3389">Jerusalem</char>, in the <char style="w" strong="H8145">second</char> <char style="w" strong="H2320">month</char>, <char style="w" strong="H2490">began</char> <char style="w" strong="H2216">Zerubbabel</char> the <char style="w" strong="H1121">son</char> of <char style="w" strong="H7597">Shealtiel</char>, and <char style="w" strong="H3442">Jeshua</char> the <char style="w" strong="H1121">son</char> of <char style="w" strong="H3136">Jozadak</char>, and the <char style="w" strong="H7605">remnant</char> of their <char style="w" strong="H0251">brethren</char> the <char style="w" strong="H3548">priests</char> and the <char style="w" strong="H3881">Levites</char>, and all they that were come <char style="w" strong="H0935">out</char> of the <char style="w" strong="H7628">captivity</char> unto <char style="w" strong="H3389">Jerusalem</char>; and <char style="w" strong="H5975">appointed</char> the <char style="w" strong="H3881">Levites</char>, from <char style="w" strong="H6242">twenty</char> <char style="w" strong="H8141">years</char> <char style="w" strong="H1121">old</char> and <char style="w" strong="H4605">upward</char>, to set <char style="w" strong="H5329">forward</char> the <char style="w" strong="H4399">work</char> of the <char style="w" strong="H1004">house</char> of the <char style="nd"><char style="w" strong="H3068">LORD</char></char>. <verse eid="EZR 3:8" /><verse number="9" style="v" sid="EZR 3:9" />Then <char style="w" strong="H5975">stood</char> <char style="w" strong="H3442">Jeshua</char> <char style="add">with</char> his <char style="w" strong="H1121">sons</char> and his <char style="w" strong="H0251">brethren</char>, <char style